    <div id="I119_sys_txt" class="sys_txt" style="margin:0px; padding:0px; color:; font:; background-color:;"><H1 id=h2s1>Blue-green Algae</H1> 
<P><STRONG>Blue-Green Algae in the Sudbury &amp; District Health Unit Area: </STRONG>If you suspect that blue-green algae is present in a waterway, <A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/contact/locations.asp?lang=0"><FONT color=#0066cc>report it to the Sudbury &amp; District Health Unit</FONT></A>. People who use waterways that have blue-green algae should <A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=2865&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=1805"><FONT color=#0066cc>take precautions</FONT></A>.</P> 
<H2 id=h2s1>Waterways Where Blue-Green Algae Has Been Identified</H2> 
<P><STRONG>By Area</STRONG></P> 
<P><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23322&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12812"><FONT color=#0066cc>City of Sudbury</FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23322&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12757"><FONT color=#0066cc>Greater Sudbury</FONT></A> <BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12759"><FONT color=#0066cc>Sudbury East </FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12760"><FONT color=#0066cc>Manitoulin Island</FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12761"><FONT color=#0066cc>Espanola </FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12762"><FONT color=#0066cc>Chapleau</FONT></A></P> 
<P><STRONG>By Year</STRONG></P> 
<P><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12763"><FONT color=#0066cc>2006 </FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12764"><FONT color=#0066cc>2007 </FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12765"><FONT color=#0066cc>2008</FONT></A> <BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12766"><FONT color=#0066cc>2009 </FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12767"><FONT color=#0066cc>2010 </FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23314&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=12768"><FONT color=#0066cc>2011</FONT></A><BR><A href="http://www.sdhu.com/content/health_hazards/doc.asp?folder=23322&amp;parent=274&amp;lang=0&amp;doc=13083"><FONT color=#0066cc>2012</FONT></A>&nbsp;</P></div>
    
